#: ../source/includes/steps/2.6-upgrade-replica-set.rst:28
msgid ""
"Upgrade the :term:`secondary` members of the set one at a time by "
"shutting down the :binary:`~bin.mongod` and replacing the 2.4 binary with"
" the 2.6 binary. After upgrading a :binary:`~bin.mongod` instance, wait "
"for the member to recover to ``SECONDARY`` state before upgrading the "
"next instance. To check the member's state, issue :method:`rs.status()` "
"in the :binary:`~bin.mongo` shell."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/steps/2.6-upgrade-replica-set.rst:26
msgid "Step 1: Upgrade secondary members of the replica set."
