#: ../source/includes/steps/2.6-upgrade-replica-set.rst:46
#: ../source/includes/steps/2.6-upgrade-replica-set.rst:62
msgid ""
"Use :method:`rs.stepDown()` in the :binary:`~bin.mongo` shell to step "
"down the :term:`primary` and force the set to :ref:`failover <replica-"
"set-failover>`. :method:`rs.stepDown()` expedites the failover procedure "
"and is preferable to shutting down the primary directly."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/steps/2.6-upgrade-replica-set.rst:60
msgid "Step 2: Step down the replica set primary."
